     H            Y.
     F** CHKR46 **************************************
     F* CHECK SYSTEM AVAILABEL FLAG                  *
     F* CREATE DATE : 2018.08.24                     *
     F* AUTHOR      : J.WATANABE                     *
     F************************************************
     FCHKPW46 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FAB#PPCK IF  E           K        DISK
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
      *  CALLING SEQ.
     C*                    CALL 'CHKR46'
     C*                    PARM           $RTN    1
      *   OUT $RTN  :  1A Y/N (SYSTEM AVAILABLE FLAG)
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
     I* SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *--------------------------------------------------
      *  MAIN ROUTINE
      *--------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
      * CHECK EXCEPTIONAL USER
     C           #USER     IFNE 'QSECOFR'
     C           #USER     ANDNE'QPGMR'
     C           #USER     ANDNE'I0023'
     C           #USER     ANDNE'I0777'
     C           #USER     ANDNE'I0778'
     C                     GOTO #ENDP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * RETRIEVE SYSTEM TIME
     C                     TIME           WSDT
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       $RTN
      *
     C                     MOVEL'ACTIVE'  $KEY   10
     C           $KEY      CHAINAB#PPCK              90
      *
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
     C           CKSFLG    ANDEQ'N'
     C                     EXFMTWIN01
     C                     MOVE 'N'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           #ENDP     TAG
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
